request.description:
Returns the full transcript of a conversation, ordered by timestamp.

**Auth:** `agent.view` permission required.

**Response:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "data": [
    { "id": "01JT...", "role": "user", "content": "Hello, I need help", "timestamp": "2026-04-21T18:00:05+00:00" },
    { "id": "01JT...", "role": "assistant", "content": "Of course! How can I help?", "timestamp": "2026-04-21T18:00:06+00:00" }
  ]
}
```
